data.description: Prepare to be wowed as you walk into this stunning open concept ranch home. This 3 bed 2.5 bath house offers a beautifully upgraded kitchen with quartz countertops as well as a spacious living area beside it. Just off the kitchen is a family room that gets an abundance of natural light that leads to a large deck. 3 nice sized bedrooms accompanied by 2 full baths on the main level along with laundry. Additional living space in the finished lower level where you find a spacious rec room with a half bath and a den. Park-like yard with a bar for summer fun! Don't let this one slip away, come see it today!
